
1. What new improvements were introduced in Gemini 3.0?
ANSWER:-

     Gemini 3.0 ne speed, accuracy aur reasoning ko kaafi improve kiya hai. Is version mein model more stable aur efficient ban gaya hai, especially coding, long-context data processing, aur multimodal tasks ke liye. Google ne memory handling, response quality aur overall performance ko bhi upgrade kiya hai taake model complex tasks ko smoothly handle kar sake.

2. How does Gemini 3.0 improve coding & automation workflows?
ANSWER:-
      Gemini 3.0 coding workflows ko faster aur zyada reliable banata hai. Yeh code likhne, debug karne aur automation scripts generate karne mein pehle se better suggestions deta hai. Model complex code samajhne mein strong ho gaya hai, jisse developers ko repetitive tasks automate karne aur project development jaldi karne mein help milti hai.


3. How does Gemini 3.0 improve multimodal understanding?
      Gemini 3.0 ka multimodal system upgraded hai, jisme model text, image, audio, aur code ko ek saath samajh sakta hai. Yeh version images aur documents ko zyada accurate tarike se interpret karta hai, aur mixed inputs (jaise text + screenshot) par better explanations de sakta hai. Overall, model real-world inputs ko naturally understand karta hai.

4. Name any two developer tools introduced with Gemini 3.0.
      Gemini API updates – jisse developers easily advanced models ko apni apps mein integrate kar sakte hain.

      Gemini Code Assist (updated version) – jo coding, refactoring aur debugging mein smart assistance deta hai.
